//{{{ 2 == Getting Started With Test Suites
[[_getting_started_with_test_suites]]
== Getting Started With Test Suites
:fn-aggregate: footnote:[total, accumulative]

//{{{ image::./images/chapter-8-4.png
[#img-chapter]
[link=./images/chapter-8-4.png]
